
Case 1 
1. no config for etags or xref. -y
2. restart emacs -y 
3. visit tags table -y 
4. visit file -y 
5. hit a tag, not found -y 
6. M-x xref-etags-mode - enable -y 
7. tag found in xref window - y 
8. M-x xref-etags-mode - disable - y
9. new tag found in xref window -y 
10. M-x xref-etags-mode - enable  -y 
11. new tag found in xref window -y

Case 2 
1. all three hooks set - y
2. restart emacs - y
3. visit tags table - y 
4. visit file - y
5. hit a tag, not found -y
6. M-x xref-etags-mode - disable - y
7. tag found in xref window - y 
8. M-x xref-etags-mode - enable -y 
9. new tag found in xref window -y
10. visit a new file -y 
11. M-. new tag - not found  -y
12. M-x xref-etags-mode - disable -y
13. M-. new tag - found -y 
14. M-x xref-etags-mode - enabled -y
15. M-. new tag found - y
16. M-x xref-etags-mode - disabled - y
17. M-. new tag found - y